title: A catch up with Evgenia Medvedeva
description:
Evgenia Medvedeva is a two-time Olympic silver medallist figure skater. Recently - she's taken a step away from competition to concentrate on some incredible shows in Russia. She sat down with Katerina Kuznetsova at the Rostelecom Cup to talk about missing competition, her relationship with social media, and who she would invite to her dinner party.

Nathan Chen Podcast
